div.h3: MMS is a grades 5-8 school in Medway, Maine. With a student population of a little over one hundred, we serve the communities of Medway, East Millinocket, and Woodville. Despite our size, we are proud to offer our students many wonderful opportunities, academic, athletic, and in the arts. Students and their education are our top priority!
